Maintainer: Mario Limonciello <superm1@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dkms
Standards-Version: 4.6.0

Package: amdxdna-dkms
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms (>= 2.1.0.0)
Recommends: linux-headers-generic | linux-headers
Description: DKMS source for AMD XDNA NPU driver
 This package provides the AMD XDNA NPU (Neural Processing Unit) kernel
 driver and firmware in DKMS format. The package supports kernels 6.14,
 6.17, and 6.18, specifically designed for Ubuntu 24.04 LTS kernel variants.
 .
 Supported devices:
  - AMD Ryzen AI (Phoenix, Hawk Point): PCI ID 1502:00
  - AMD Ryzen AI (Strix Point): PCI ID 17f0:10
  - AMD Ryzen AI (Strix Halo): PCI ID 17f0:11
 .
 The module will be automatically built for each installed kernel via DKMS.
